TruthSeal™ — Re-Elevation Plan v1.0

Date: 2025-10-15
Author: Dr Nickolay Traykov (Prof. h.c.), Bulgarian-Australian Founder of THT Protocol™
Classification: Public-Safe Strategic Roadmap

Purpose

To execute the four institutional milestones required to maintain and expand the A $ 11 billion sovereign valuation baseline defined in the Valuation Integrity & Funding Assurance Memo v1.0.

⸻

Phase Milestones

1 — Foundation Launch (Pre-Christmas 2025)

Objective: Formally launch the TruthSeal Sovereign Ledger Foundation as a non-profit trust.
Deliverables: Governance charter • Public website • Initial advisory board seated • Open-ledger demo online.
Impact: Valuation multiplier × 2 (≈ A $ 5.4 B).

⸻

2 — Public Ledger Sandbox (Q1 2026)

Objective: Deploy pilot Integrity Ledger with ≥ 1 million verifiable records anchored via Polygon PoS + OTS.
Deliverables: Sandbox API • Developer dashboard • Public audit access • DAO feedback loop.
Impact: Valuation multiplier × 3 (≈ A $ 8.1 B).

⸻

3 — SDK Integration (Q2 2026)

Objective: Integrate THT/TruthSeal Integrity SDK with OpenAI and Anthropic for compliance and traceability.
Deliverables: SDK release • documentation • verified benchmarks • joint public statement.
Impact: Valuation multiplier × 5 (≈ A $ 13.5 B).

⸻

4 — Institutional MoUs (Q3 2026)

Objective: Secure three Memoranda of Understanding with academic, governmental and industrial partners.
Deliverables: Signed MoUs • press release • blockchain-anchored proofs on Integrity Ledger.
Impact: Valuation multiplier × 10 → A $ 11 B confirmed sovereign status.

⸻

Governance and Audit
	•	Oversight: TruthSeal Institutional Board under THT Protocol Authority.
	•	Audit Frequency: Every 30 days or upon material change ≥ ± 5 %.
	•	Reporting: Automatic submission to Integrity Ledger and public repository.
